1. WHAT THE APP IS
────────────────────

Psyche Library is a research aggregator. It searches public academic databases (PubMed, CrossRef, Europe PMC, OpenAlex, Semantic Scholar, DOAJ, arXiv) and the open web, summarizes findings with AI, and lets you save, bookmark, and review articles. It is NOT a clinical decision-support tool, NOT a replacement for primary literature reading, and NOT a substitute for licensed clinical judgment.

────────────────────
2. AI-GENERATED CONTENT
────────────────────

AI summaries and literature reviews are produced by large language models (Anthropic Claude). They can be inaccurate, miss context, or hallucinate citations. ALWAYS verify any clinical, diagnostic, or treatment claim against the underlying source articles before relying on it. You are solely responsible for your use of AI-generated text.

────────────────────
